description_en: second (generally maternal) family name in Spanish names (do not use for other double barrelled names) and in some French names.

description_zh: 一家公司或组织的下属机构部门；通常是完全拥有的单立集团。与“业务部门”（P199）相对应。母组织（P749）的逆属性。
description_en: subsidiary of a company or organization; generally a fully owned separate corporation. Compare with "business division" (P199). Opposite of parent organization (P749).

description_en: underlying or immediate cause of death.  Underlying cause (e.g. car accident, stomach cancer) preferred. Use 'manner of death' (P1196) for broadest category, e.g. natural causes, accident, homicide, suicide
